sections.heading: Mobile slaughtering units; custom slaughtering; brand inspections3-1339
sections.text: Mobile slaughtering units; custom slaughtering; brand inspectionsA. A mobile slaughtering unit or a locker plant slaughtering livestock on a custom basis shall notify the local livestock officer or inspector before any slaughter
